      "patchset_number": 2,
      "line": null,
      "message": "I think it would be better to have two separate test plans and two separate set-up instructions\n1. One for cps-core\n2. One for ncmp and onap-dmi-plugin\n\nCurrently, we are testing completely different things in the same testplan.\n\nFor later : We can also have filters to run only relevant test-cases (defined by the which project has been updates) based on maven modules changes, but run all test cases when merge.",
